                          <span id="subjectNode_9021526" style="font-weight:bold;">RE: Overall Chances of Upgrades</span><br>
                          Mar 3 2008, 11:37 AM EST<br>
                          <span class="threadText" id="textNode_9021526">xD yeah you won&#39;t get a +5 weapon after the second try, the upgrade is based on a selection of numbers by the game itself. the numbers from 1 to 100 &lt; those are the chances. 50% chance means that if the computer selects 1 of the 50 positive numbers in that scale the upgrade will be succesful; if the game selects 1 of the negative 50 numbers then the weapon will be destroyed.<br>
                          <br>
